            "id": 6256246,
            "title": "〈美股盤後〉黑五開跑 美股三大指數收高 英特爾飆漲10% ",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股感恩節休市一天後，在周五 (28 日)「黑色星期五」這一天恢復交易，交易時間比平日提早在美東凌晨 1 點收盤，交投也比平日清淡，最終在對聯準會 (Fed)12 月的降息預期中上漲，距離歷史高點只差一小步。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6256246/l/9ee269a61832fe1e4b3f16a53aa3f398.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈美股盤後〉黑五開跑 美股三大指數收高 英特爾飆漲10%  (圖:Reuters/TPG)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股漲幅在 0.5%-0.6% 之間。英特爾在科技股中漲勢最猛，亞馬遜和沃爾瑪則隨年底購物季開跑而勁揚。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>芝商所 (CME) 因資料中心散熱問題，稍早曾暫停交易數小時，這個狀況雖然在美股開盤前已經排除，卻也讓一些投資人選擇在場邊觀望，使漲幅受抑制。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>受益於科技股反彈，美股在感恩節本周均有明顯漲幅，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊</a>一周上漲 3.18%，標普 500 上漲 3.73%，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克</a>上漲 4.91%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>本周五也是 11 月最後一個交易日，三大指數中的<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊</a>、標普 11 月交出連續第七個月月線收紅的紀錄，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊</a>漲 0.32%，標普漲 0.13%。唯獨<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克</a> 11 月下跌 1.51%，終結連七個月漲勢，反映對人工智慧 (AI) 未來獲利能力、以及科技股高估值的疑慮。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股周五 (28 日) 主要指數表現： </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊工業指數</a>上漲 289.30 點，或 0.61%，收 47,716.42 點。</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克綜合指數</a>上漲 151.00 點，或 0.65%，收 23,365.69 點。</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">標普 500 指數</a>上漲 36.48 點，或 0.54%，收 6,849.09 點。 </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數上漲 125.69 點，或 1.82%，收 7,025.15 點。</li>\n<li>NYSE FANG+ 指數上漲 145.74 點，或 0.88%，收 16,624.74 點。</li>\n</ul></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img alt=\"圖取自finviz\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6256246/l/ab21249266a5639f93f9bb56ca814f35.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption>圖取自 finviz</figcaption>\n</figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>標普 11 大類股多上漲，僅健康照護類股收黑。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><h6>焦點個股</h6></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>NYSE FANG + 指數中的科技五大巨頭。Meta(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:META:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/META\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">META-US</a>)上漲 2.26%；蘋果 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AAPL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AAPL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AAPL-US</a>) 上漲 0.47%；Alphabet(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:GOOGL:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/GOOGL\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">GOOGL-US</a>)上漲 0.07%；微軟 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MSFT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MSFT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MSFT-US</a>) 上漲 1.34%；亞馬遜 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMZN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMZN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMZN-US</a>) 上漲 1.77%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費半</a>成分股走高。英特爾 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>) 狂漲 10.3%；Analog(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ADI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ADI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ADI-US</a>)上漲 2.88%；美光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>) 漲 2.7%；安謀 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ARM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ARM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ARM-US</a>) 攀升 2.22%。輝達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>) 唯一收黑，下跌 1.81%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台股 ADR 普遍上揚。台積電 ADR(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 上漲 0.53%；日月光 ADR(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ASX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ASX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ASX-US</a>) 上漲 3.82%；聯電 ADR(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:UMC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/UMC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">UMC-US</a>) 漲 1.77%；中華電信 ADR(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CHT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CHT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CHT-US</a>) 下跌 0.24%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><strong>持續更新中...</strong></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p> </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"warning\"><br/>\n數字皆為截稿前更新，請依照實際報價為主</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
